🤖 Replit Agent in early access


The Replit Agent is now available to all core subscribers in early access. 
That means you might run into a bug or two, but bear with us—we think you'll 
get value from it already.

 You can think about the Agent like a pair programmer. It configures your 
development environment, installs dependencies, executes code, and evenhelps 
you deploy.

Now, with only a few sentences and a few minutes, you can take an application 
from idea to deployment. Here, you can see the agent writing code across 
several files:



But lots of tools can write code—that's what sets the agent apart. It can 
install dependencies and configure everything you need to get your app running.

 When that's all said-and-done, it can even help you deploy your app.

